<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-40-1176 </DOCNO><TEXT>New experimental data on nuclei with large neutron excess, combined withan earlier formula which connected binding energies of neutrons in suchnuclei with those of protons in mirror neutron-deficient nuclei, givequite reliable predictions of the properties of four isotopes which areexpected to manifest two-proton radioactivity, /sup 22/Si, /sup 31/Ar,/sup 39/Ti and /sup 42/Cr.</TEXT></DOC>